schema.description: Complete details for an event subscription.

eventType.description: Type of event to listen for. Can be one of `create`, `delete`, `deletedForPrivacy`, or `propertyChange`.

propertyName.description: The internal name of the property being monitored for changes. Only applies when `eventType` is `propertyChange`.
